%^BOLD%^-=%^BLUE%^Protection Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

This domain grants its users the ability to protect themselves and their surroundings in various ways. Not only will it offer some protection in battle, but it will also aid in preventing certain magical spells and effects.

Clerics with the Protection Domain receive a passive +4 bonus to their Armor Class.

The protection domain contains the following spells:

Divine Favor, Shield Other, Resist Energy, Lesser Globe of Invulnerability, Invisibility Purge, Repulsion, Spell Turning, Mind Blank, Dimensional Lock

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kreysneothosies

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
